<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>safe against something • safe from something</xh5><p> <i>safe against something—</i>protected from possible dangers (such as fire, etc.) should they happen: I try to make sure my house is as <u>safe against</u> hurricanes as possible.</p><p> <i>safe from something—</i>said of dangers that cannot possibly harm a person or thing: A person once infected with the smallpox is <u>safe from</u> having it a second time.</p> </entry>
